Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.72,0:02:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,影 Shadow 2
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.46,0:02:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,獸道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.27,0:02:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,再右邊一點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.77,0:02:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不 左邊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.01,0:02:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.18,0:02:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,這是照相機
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.81,0:02:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,照相機
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.85,0:02:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,可以把看到的東西直接拍到裡面喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.65,0:02:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我上次去異人館的時候借來的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.46,0:02:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,自從黑船過來以後，就有好多新奇東西進入江戶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.56,0:02:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,要拍了喔，不要動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.50,0:02:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.00,0:02:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啦 不要動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.81,0:03:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,是孫六
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.42,0:03:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,死了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.32,0:03:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.42,0:03:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,還沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.36,0:03:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,但是. . .
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.56,0:03:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,能這樣處處妨礙我們的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.63,0:03:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,究竟會是誰呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.70,0:03:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,對方好像故意捉弄我們一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.50,0:03:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,眼神中懷有怨恨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.21,0:03:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,怨恨?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.98,0:03:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,真是冤枉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.52,0:03:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,這也是我們忍者的宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.52,0:03:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,華龍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.02,0:03:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.89,0:03:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,若是那個人再出現
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.46,0:03:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不用管 把他收拾掉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.64,0:04:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.24,0:04:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,葵大人 孫六大人來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.47,0:04:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,叫他進來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.14,0:04:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼小的告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.82,0:04:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,和服批發商大黑屋利兵衛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.86,0:04:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,用任何手段，方法都行/n 只要把他殺死
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.56,0:04:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,可是孫六
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.20,0:04:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,利兵衛不是一向與你很好嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.54,0:04:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,所以更不能讓他活命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.51,0:04:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,叛徒是非死不可的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.92,0:04:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,叛徒?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.32,0:04:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,那傢伙搶我們生意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.49,0:05:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,啊. . .在多的就不能說了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.70,0:05:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,這是訂金
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.07,0:05:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼您願意接受委託囉?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.35,0:05:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,這不是華龍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.85,0:05:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,上次妳做得很漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.10,0:05:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,因該可以吧 以我們的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.17,0:05:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,孫六
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.84,0:05:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以對華龍下手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.34,0:05:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,除了華龍之外
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.38,0:05:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有人像她這樣活著回來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.92,0:06:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.69,0:06:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼大黑屋先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.53,0:06:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.63,0:06:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,麻煩盡快把對方收拾掉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.30,0:06:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.47,0:06:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,放心 一切包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.44,0:06:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,保證不會失敗的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.71,0:07:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,真是 您這人未了錢什麼事都幹的出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.42,0:07:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,真是可怕的人物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.06,0:07:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,您太愛開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.97,0:07:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝招待 那麼我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.24,0:07:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.39,0:07:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,光琳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.06,0:07:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,下面有忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.76,0:07:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.84,0:07:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,怎樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.81,0:08:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,逃走了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.51,0:08:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,這傢伙逃的很快
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.15,0:08:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你說什麼悠哉話 快追啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.92,0:08:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,一定要把他殺死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.69,0:08:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.59,0:08:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,到底是什麼人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.43,0:08:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,混蛋 別讓人逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.02,0:08:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.56,0:08:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,利兵衛是孫六先生的勁敵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.20,0:09:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,鴉逗女 到了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.21,0:09:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,難道. . .
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.85,0:09:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,她果然沒有死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.79,0:10:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,為何他會來利兵衛這裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.53,0:10:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,到底. . .
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.90,0:10:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,他想要幹什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.47,0:10:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不愧是大黑屋 想的很周到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.70,0:10:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,最近的商人都不懂禮儀 所以令人傷腦筋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.35,0:10:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,這個看起來很可口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.87,0:11:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,還是處女嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.71,0:11:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不要. . .
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.32,0:11:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.33,0:11:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,這肌膚真是美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.87,0:11:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不錯 這個太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.40,0:12:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,被察覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.61,0:13:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,殺 把他殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.97,0:13:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,斷念吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.25,0:13:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,這是. . .
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.02,0:13:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.56,0:13:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,現在才注意到已經太遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.56,0:13:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,毒藥因該快發作了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.91,0:14:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,別那麼急
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.91,0:14:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,果然是女人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.25,0:14:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.42,0:14:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼年輕的生命就. . .
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.92,0:14:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,這個誘人喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.76,0:14:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,讓你死前享受一下好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.36,0:14:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,這個真不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.11,0:14:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,這個. . .我快融化了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.85,0:14:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下 這次換我送你上天堂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.56,0:14:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,怎樣 這招很棒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.33,0:15:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多要開動了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.48,0:15:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,裡面真緊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.66,0:17:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,又是那個夢. . .
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.04,0:17:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,妳醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.94,0:17:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.01,0:17:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,儀助
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.82,0:17:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,喝下這個會好過一些
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.25,0:17:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,毒已經除掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.72,0:17:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不過 可能還會有些痛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.60,0:17:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那個男人呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.90,0:17:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.50,0:17:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,愚蠢的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.67,0:18:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,他若直接殺掉妳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.41,0:18:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,就什麼事也沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.31,0:18:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,繃帶很快就能解開了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.25,0:18:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,請問這裡是. . .
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.39,0:18:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我的住處 不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.26,0:18:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,儀助先生 謝謝你的照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.73,0:18:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,妳現在不方便行動
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.77,0:18:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不 追殺我的人會過來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.80,0:18:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我在這裡會給你添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.37,0:18:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不用擔心 這已是租的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.21,0:18:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我很快就離開了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.81,0:18:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,以後因該會再碰面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.59,0:18:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你要愛惜自己的命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.07,0:19:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.11,0:19:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,像天女一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.11,0:19:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我從沒見過這麼美的肌膚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.15,0:19:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,妳到底是打哪來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.98,0:19:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,是天上還是地獄呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.52,0:19:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,算了 何者都無妨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.96,0:19:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我還要讓妳做更多的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.03,0:19:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,為我做更多的事. . .
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.23,0:20:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,怎樣 你也喝一口吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.43,0:20:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,西洋酒是很難弄到的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.80,0:20:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不敢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.47,0:20:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,給我這麼卑下的人喝這種酒太浪費了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.41,0:20:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,說的跟真的似的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.31,0:20:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.61,0:20:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,利兵衛的事情辦的怎樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.48,0:20:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,因該沒有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.75,0:20:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,確定嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.59,0:20:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,是 絕對不會錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.69,0:20:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.50,0:20:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,是. . .
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.03,0:20:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,德川的天下快結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.87,0:20:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,可是. . .
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.87,0:20:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.77,0:20:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,孫六
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.44,0:20:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你可要小心幕府的狗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.45,0:20:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.79,0:21:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,結束了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.06,0:21:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.90,0:21:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,痛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.16,0:21:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不 沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.37,0:21:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,妳不會寂寞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.19,0:21:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,鴉逗女 妳到哪裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.80,0:21:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我說過不可擅自行動的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.97,0:21:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,儀助
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.97,0:21:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,幫我洗掉 儀助
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.09,0:22:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,臨兵鬥者皆陣列在前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.90,0:22:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡也有伏棋 怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.14,0:22:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你的伏棋太多了 沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.24,0:22:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,誰說的 多安插幾個的話. . .
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.01,0:22:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,雙單雙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.61,0:22:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你輸了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.32,0:22:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.64,0:22:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,利兵衛不在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.12,0:23:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.55,0:23:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,妳的傷好像完全好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.16,0:23:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.59,0:23:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,妳也是忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.50,0:23:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我實在不想與妳交手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.77,0:23:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你若妨礙我 我就得殺你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.34,0:24:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我說過 要妳愛惜生命
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.25,0:24:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,華龍 聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.05,0:24:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,快離開這個工作
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.19,0:24:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,現在不能殺死利兵衛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.49,0:25:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你受孫六所託來殺利兵衛
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.86,0:25:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,這個我全知道
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.53,0:25:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,孫六不可信任
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.37,0:25:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,世界正在改變
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.94,0:25:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,往你不知道的方向
